title: IGNITE e-Sports looking for Brisbane Players
body:
Freshly new Internet Gaming Cafe from Korea re-located in South Brisbane, Macgregor is looking for local players in the area who are willing to play under it's label. Ignite e-Sports will provide all gaming equipment & free gaming time for scrims/ solo que etc (anything to help the players reach their full potential). Preferred Diamond+ players and will hold try-outs.

Roles open:
Coach - Taken
Top laner - N/A
Jungle - Taken
Mid - N/A
ADC - Taken
Support - Taken
